{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_001", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "老李在第一起谋杀案的现场发现了一张便利贴，上面写着'SORRY'。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "'SORRY'是凶手留下的签名。每一起案件都有一张'SORRY'纸条，这是连环杀手的标志。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_002", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "死者的手机上有一个未接来电，来电显示是'妈妈'。但死者母亲三年前就去世了。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "'妈妈'是凶手备注的假名——凶手是死者最亲近的人。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_003", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "被害人家中少了一张照片，相框还在但照片被取走了。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "被取走的照片上有一个关键人物——就是凶手本人。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_004", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "嫌疑人提供了完美的不在场证明——但证明人是他妻子。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "妻子在撒谎帮她丈夫隐瞒——她以为丈夫出轨了，实际上丈夫是去杀人。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_005", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "法医在死者胃中发现了一枚没有消化的戒指。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "戒指是结婚戒指，内侧刻着'2002.6.15'。那天发生了另一起失踪案。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_006", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "老李在走访时发现所有邻居都说死者'人很好，从不和人来往'。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "'从不和人来往'意味着没有人真正了解死者——他的身份可能是伪造的。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_007", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "案发现场的窗帘被拉到了一半——这是死者从不做的事情。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "凶手在作案后拉上了窗帘，因为他不想被对面楼看到。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_008", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "死者的电脑上有一个加密文件夹，密码是'justice'。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "文件夹中是证据——死者生前掌握了某个黑帮的犯罪证据，这就是他被杀的原因。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_009", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "老李在第二次案发现场闻到了和第一次相同的香水味。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "香水味来自女凶手——她用同一种香水，在现场留下了气味证据。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_010", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "受害者的指甲缝中有皮肤组织，DNA鉴定后却发现是失踪十几年的通缉犯。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "通缉犯和受害者是父子关系——儿子在替父亲顶罪。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_011", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "老李在审讯时说了一句话：'凶手是个左撇子。'所有线索都指向这个判断。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "但凶手其实是右撇子——老李故意说错来观察嫌疑人的反应。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_012", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "现场的血迹中有几滴不属于受害者的血——但DNA库中没有匹配。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "血是凶手多年前献血的记录——当时他还没犯罪，DNA没有被录入犯罪数据库。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_013", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "死者最后一通电话是打给了一个空号。但通话记录显示持续了三分钟。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "空号实际上是某个秘密号码的伪装——三分钟的通话足以传递关键信息。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_014", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "小偷在盗窃时发现主人家中有一张照片，照片上的人是他认识的。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "照片上的人是小区保安——他不是小偷，而是受保安指使来销毁证据的。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_015", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "死者的日记中有一页被撕掉了，后面的页上有笔压痕。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "老李用铅笔在下一页上涂出了压痕——上面写着一个日期和'对不起'。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_016", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "停车场监控发现死者的车在案发当晚进出过五次。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "五次进出对应五个不同的人——死者那晚在停车场见了五个'朋友'。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_017", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "老李发现三位死者都曾在同一家餐厅用过餐。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "那家餐厅的老板就是凶手——他和每一个死者都有私人恩怨。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_018", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "证人说他'看到凶手穿着红色衣服'，但当晚的监控是黑白的。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "证人在撒谎——黑白监控根本看不出红色。他要么是凶手本人，要么在包庇。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_019", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "老李在警局档案中发现了一桩十年前未破的悬案，手法和现在的一模一样。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "凶手沉寂了十年——他在监狱里坐了十年牢，刚出狱就又犯案了。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_020", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "死者手中握着一张撕碎的电影票，被拼起来后日期是案发当天。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "电影票是凶手故意放在死者手中的——他在挑衅警方。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_021", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "老李发现死者的手机步数记录显示案发时走了8000步。但死者是坐轮椅的。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "手机被绑在凶手的腿上——凶手不知道死者的步数记录会暴露自己。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_022", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "被害人的猫在案发后一直蹲在衣柜前叫。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "衣柜里藏着一件带血的凶器——是猫目睹了凶手藏匿凶器。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_023", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "现场有一根头发，经检测属于一个'已经死亡三年的人'。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "那个人没有死——他伪造了自己的死亡，这次回来复仇了。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_024", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "老李发现每个案发现场都有一个小孩子的玩具——弹珠。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "弹珠是凶手的标志——他每次作案都会留下一颗弹珠，纪念他死去的儿子。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_025", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "死者的银行记录显示案发当天她取出了一大笔现金。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "现金是给凶手的赎金——但她还是被杀了。凶手拿了钱但没有放人。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_026", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "凶手在邮件中写道'你们会找到她的尸体'。用的是'她'——警方没公开死者性别。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "凶手暴露了自己是熟人——只有认识死者的人才知道死者是女性。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_027", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "老李在整理旧案卷时发现一桩案件的物证标签被调换了。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "有人故意调包了证物来陷害一个无辜的人——那个'凶手'坐了十五年冤狱。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_028", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "新来的实习生第一次看尸检照片就吐了，但他是法医专业毕业的。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "实习生在学校看到的所有照片都是黑白处理的——他没见过真正的血腥照片。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_029", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "被害人的手机定位显示案发时她在A地，但监控拍到她同时在B地。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "有两个一模一样的人——死者的双胞胎妹妹，没人知道她的存在。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_030", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "凶器上的指纹是模糊的，只能看出是右手拇指。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "模糊是因为凶手戴着手套按压了指纹——他想嫁祸给有前科的人。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_031", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "老李发现每次案发前一周都会有人拨打一个相同的电话号码，然后挂断。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "那个号码是一家花店的电话——凶手用这种方式订花送给受害者，作为预告。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_032", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "死者的遗书中提到了一个名字，但被涂黑了。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "涂黑的名字是凶手——但遗书本身是伪造的，是凶手逼死者写的。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_033", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "老李发现三个受害者的生日是同一天——3月15日。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "他们在同一天过生日——三人在同一个生日派对上相识。凶手也在那个派对上。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_mystery_034", "genre": "mystery", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "警犬在案发现场嗅到了一种特殊的麻醉剂味道，但没有相关记录。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "麻醉剂是兽医用的——凶手是一名兽医。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
